(48, 'J. Wiley', 'jwiley@sampsoncc.edu', 'dmatthews@sampsoncc.edu', 'CJC 111', '2016-02-15', 1.00, '', '0000-00-00', 0.00, 0.00, 'on', '<span style="font-size: 16px;">Student will complete a discussion forum discussion question board.</span><br><span style="font-size: 16px;">Student must review the "ethics and professionalism" box on page 185 of the textbook</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">After reviewing the information about the ethics and professionalism, the student must post their individual response the discussion question posted in the discussion forum in Moodle by Thursday night. The student must then substantively respond to at least two other students in the forum by Sunday night 11:55 PM</span><p><br></p>', '', 0.00, 0.00, '', '', '', 0.00, '', '', 'inclement_weather', '', 'Jennifer Wiley', '2016-02-15', 'W. Darell Matthews', '2016-02-16', 'William J. Starling (aw)', '2016-02-18'),
(49, 'Joy Rogers', 'jrogers@sampsoncc.edu', 'cphipps@sampsoncc.edu', 'COM 110-OA', '2016-02-15', 1.50, '', '0000-00-00', 0.00, 0.00, 'on', 'Watch the "Adapting to Cultures" Video in Moodle (47 minutes);<p>Read the "Adapting to Cultures" chapter in textbook;<br><p>Respond to the "Adapting to Cultures" forum in Moodle with questions & reflection about the video watched.<br></p></p>', '', 0.00, 0.00, '', '', '', 0.00, '', '', 'inclement_weather', '', 'Joy Rogers', '2016-02-16', 'Carole Phipps', '2016-02-17', 'William J. Starling (aw)', '2016-02-18'),
(50, 'W. Darell Matthews', 'dmatthews@sampsoncc.edu', 'dmatthews@sampsoncc.edu', 'SEC150-WA', '2016-02-15', 1.50, '', '0000-00-00', 0.00, 0.00, '', '', 'on', 1.50, 1.50, 'Load-Balancing Algorithms<p><br></p><p>Different algorithms are used to make decisions on load balancing. These include random allocation, round-robin, weighted round-robin, round-robin DNS load balancing, and others. Use the Internet to research load-balancing algorithms. Create a table that lists at least give algorithms and their advantages and disadvantages. Do any of these algorithms compromise security? Write a one-page paper on your research.</p>', '', '', 0.00, '', '', 'inclement_weather', '', 'W. Darell Matthews', '2016-02-16', 'W. Darell Matthews', '2016-02-16', 'William J. Starling (aw)', '2016-02-18'),
(51, 'Susan S. Jernigan', 'sjernigan@sampsoncc.edu', 'cphipps@sampsoncc.edu', 'MAT 110-OA', '2016-02-15', 2.00, '', '0000-00-00', 0.00, 0.00, '', '', 'on', 2.00, 2.00, 'Students will complete the Chapter 2 Review Homework that is assigned through MyMathLab.', '', '', 0.00, '', '', 'inclement_weather', '', 'Susan S. Jernigan', '2016-02-16', 'Carole Phipps', '2016-02-17', 'William J. Starling (aw)', '2016-02-18'),
