><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b>8.<span style="font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></b><!--[endif]-->Whatis an abstract? Can you use quotes from the abstract in your paper?<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b>9.<span style="font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></b><!--[endif]-->Whatare the four ways to use the article?<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left:2.5in;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-2.0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><!--[if !supportLists]-->A)<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"></span><!--[endif]-->C)<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-left:2.5in;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-2.0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><!--[if !supportLists]-->B)<span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"></span><!--[endif]-->D)<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b>10.<span style="font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></b><!--[endif]-->Howcan you get a correct MLA style citation for this article?<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b>11.<span style="font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></b><!--[endif]-->Explainhow to get a copy of an article that doesnt have Full Text access.<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b>12.<span style="font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></b><!--[endif]-->Whatis the password for using NCLive at home?<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b>13.<span style="font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></b><!--[endif]-->Whatdo you do if you cant find any sources that support your point?<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b>14.<span style="font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></b><!--[endif]-->Whatdoes paraphrase mean?<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><!--[if !supportLists]--><b>15.<span style="font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></b><!--[endif]-->Whatpunctuation marks must you include when you directly quote a source?<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Now Do Some Research<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><i>For this section, goto the library start page. Youl