(108, 'Ria Westphal', 'rwestphal@sampsoncc.edu', 'cphipps@sampsoncc.edu', 'Art 111 OA', '2016-02-24', 1.50, '', '0000-00-00', 0.00, 0.00, 'on', '<p class="MsoNormal">R. Westphal <o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Art 111 OA<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Make-up Plan for 2/24/2016<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Hello everyone!<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Please make sure to view the three videos about AbstractExpressionism and Jackson Pollock to make up for our missing yet another class(those weather gods have it in for us).<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">Log into Moodle, scroll to Topic 7 and follow thedirectionssee below. We will have a classroom discussion next Wednesdaydo notforget to study for the test on Monday!!!<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">See you then,<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal">R. Westphal<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0in; line-height: 30pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><![endif]--><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 12pt 0.0001pt; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 15pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#595959"><span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: Times New Roman;"></span><!--[endif]--><!--[if mso & !supportInlineShapes & supportFields]>SHAPE * MERGEFORMAT <![endif]--><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:rect id="yui_3_17_2_3_1456329786114_4619" o:spid="_x0000_s1026" alt="Move resource" style=width:24pt;height:24pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square; mso-left-percent:-10001;mso-top-percent:-10001;mso-position-horizontal:absolute; mso-position-horizontal-relative:char;mso-position-vertical:absolute; mso-position-vertical-relative:line;mso-left-percent:-10001;mso-top-percent:-10001; v-text-anchor:top o:gfxdata="" filled="f" stroked="f"> <o:lock v:ext="edit" aspectratio="t"/> <w:wrap type="none"/> <w:anchorlock/></v:rect><![endif]--><!--[if mso & !supportInlineShapes & supportFields]><v:shape id="_x0000_i1028" type="#_x0000_t75" style=width:24pt;height:24pt> <v:imagedata croptop="-65520f" cropbottom="65520f"/></v:shape><![endif]--><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 12pt 7.5pt; text-align: center; line-height: 15pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 12pt 7.5pt; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><b><span style="font-size:36.0pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black">Jackson Pollock &Abstract Expressionism</span></b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 12pt 7.5pt; text-align: center; line-height: 15pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959;mso-no-proof:yes"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id="il_fi" o:spid="_x0000_i1027" type="#_x0000_t75" alt="http://www.jackson-pollock.org/images/jackson_pollock.jpg" style=width:150pt;height:204.75pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square> <v:imagedata src="file:///C:UsersRWESTP~1AppDataLocalTempmsohtmlclip11clip_image002.jpg"  o:title="jackson_pollock"/></v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img width="200" height="273" src="file:///C:/Users/RWESTP~1/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image003.jpg" alt="http://www.jackson-pollock.org/images/jackson_pollock.jpg" v:shapes="il_fi"><!--[endif]--></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 12pt 7.5pt; text-align: center; line-height: 15pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><i><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black">"When I am in my painting, I am not aware of what I amdoing."- Jackson Pollock</span></i><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 12pt 7.5pt; text-align: center; line-height: 15pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black">RIGHT CLICK THE LINK BELOW & OPEN IN NEW TAB</span></b><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 12pt 7.5pt; text-align: center; line-height: 15pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uy1SXVAlrDI"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uy1SXVAlrDI</span></b></a><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 12pt 7.5pt; text-align: center; line-height: 15pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959">This is a video highlighting the life and artwork of JacksonPollock. He was part of the Abstract Expressionist movement, and theystrived to express their emotions purely through paint. (It is much morecomplex, but the movie will help you understand!) Jackson was known as a cowboybecause he was from Wyoming... however; he was far from that description. Hisartwork does not fit within the 4 basic categories of Art Styles. It is amodern art form that tears away from those restricting parameters.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 12pt 7.5pt; text-align: center; line-height: 15pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959">Like many of the Abstract Expressionists, Pollock was analcoholic. Most of these artists lived "self-induced" tragedies. Infact, Jacksons alcoholism eventually caused him to lose his life.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 12pt 7.5pt; text-align: center; line-height: 15pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:"Helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:#595959">Please dont let the Abstract Expressionists give artists a badwrap... Trust me; we are not all that eccentric!<!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id="Picture_x0020_2" o:spid="_x0000_i1026" type="#_x0000_t75" alt="smile" style=width:11.25pt;height:11.25pt; visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square> <v:imagedata src="file:///C:UsersRWESTP~1AppDataLocalTempmsohtmlclip11clip_image004.gif"  o:title="smile"/></v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img border="0" width="15" height="15" src="file:///C:/Users/RWESTP~1/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image004.gif" a