(125, 'Laurie Hamilton', 'lhamilton@sampsoncc.edu', 'dmatthews@sampsoncc.edu', 'ANS 115 - Feeds & Nutrition', '2016-02-24', 1.00, '', '0000-00-00', 0.00, 0.00, '', '', 'on', 1.00, 1.00, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 7.5pt 0in; line-height: 30pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:" helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman";mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#595959;background:yellow"="">Here is your make-up assignment for February24. This should take you about 1 hour to complete.</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:" helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman";mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#595959;background:lime"="">Letsget this done by March 4.</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:" helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman";mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#595959"=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:" helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman";mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#595959"="">What do you know about Mad Cow Disease or</span><a href="https://mymoodle.sampsoncc.edu/mod/url/view.php?id=203866" title="Bovine Spongiform Encephalopathy"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:" helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman";mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#0070a8;text-decoration:none;text-underline:none"="">Bovine Spongiform Encephalopathy</span></a><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:" helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman";mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#595959"="">? Here are some video clips thatwill help you learn about BSE and prion diseases including variantCreutzfeld-Jakob Disease.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:" helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman";mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#595959"="">Below is a link to the CDCs facts on vCJD in the US andNCBAs summary of government regulations for prevention of BSE.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:" helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman";mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#595959"="">Read these either before or after you watch the videos. Thentake the short lab quiz on BSE. You may use the factsheets and any notes youtake on the video while taking the test. I will allow you to take the quiztwice to improve your grade.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt;font-family:" helvetica",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"times="" new="" roman";mso-bidi-font-family:helvetica;color:#595959"="">If you find this stuff really interesting I have includedtheone about Kuru which is OPTIONAL--its pretty long, b