(208, 'Susan Baxter', 'sbaxter@sampsoncc.edu', 'bstarling@sampsoncc.edu', 'EDU 271 HB', '2016-06-29', 2.00, '', '0000-00-00', 0.00, 0.00, 'on', '<p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt">As we prepare for the VirtualFieldtrip Assignment, we will first gather information about how we might makethe virtual trip  will we use streaming video or virtual reality? Then, we will look at creating a plan (thisis where your text will come in handy).Finally, we will pull it all together and create a Virtual FieldTrip. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><b><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><b><span style="font-size:14.0pt">Some Background Information<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><b><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Streaming Video andVirtual Reality</b><span style="font-size:8.0pt;font-family:"Arial",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";display:none;mso-hide:all">Top ofForm</span><b><o:p></o:p></b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Technology has so much to offer us. We can usestreaming video and virtual reality to really add some pizazz to ourclassrooms. Both of these items require media plug-ins or downloads andalso a high bandwidth connection. In other words - not possible with adial-up internet connection. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">We will look at both items individually below. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black">Streaming Video</span></b><b><span style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""> <o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">There are many great free videos out there for educationaluse.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Here is a popular site that requires that you shop for yourvideo ahead of time, preview well and bookmark. This site has plenty ofinappropriate materials, so you need to be cautious.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://www.youtube.com/"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">www.youtube.com</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">There is a similar site that only host educationalinformation. It is a bit safer.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://www.teachertube.com/"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">www.teachertube.com</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Some PBS educational videos:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://media.nclive.org/"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">http://media.nclive.org/</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Here are some cool science videos:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://kids.nationalgeographic.com/kids/videos/"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">http://kids.nationalgeographic.com/kids/videos/</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Here are some Beatrix Potter stories on video:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://bigbible.org/children/"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">http://bigbible.org/children/</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black">Virtual Reality</span></b><b><span style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""> <o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Virtual Reality can open more doors than I can describe inthis short module. You can view and experience things from all over theworld in your classroom through this technology. Here are just a fewexamples of the types of things this technology has to offer.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">See what is happening in other areas:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://www.earthcam.com/"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">http://www.earthcam.com/</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">This site allows you to see things from all over the worldin present time due to webcam technology. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Go to the San Diego Zoo!! They have some greatwebcams: </span><a href="http://www.sandiegozoo.org/videos/"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">http://www.sandiegozoo.org/videos/</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Besides seeing what is going on elsewhere, you can usevirtual reality to go on a virtual field trip. Wish you had the money totake the class to the countrys capital? Go electronically. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://www.senate.gov/vtour/"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">http://www.senate.gov/vtour/</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Museum Field trip?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://www.education-world.com/a_curr/curr057.shtml"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">http://www.education-world.com/a_curr/curr057.shtml</span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Here is an excellent example of a 4-H garden field trip:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><a href="http://4hgarden.msu.edu/kidstour/tour.html"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue">http://4hgarden.msu.edu/kidstour/tour.html</span></a><u><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:blue"><o:p></o:p></span></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Hopefully this stimulates some ideas regarding the virtualtravel to a destination. Now refer toyour textbook  specifically page 62, the Tech Tools & Tips box entitledVirtual Field Trips to read the 6 tips for designing a successful virtual trip.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Now, it is time to put your Virtual Field Trip Together.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"">Here is what you need to include in your final product thatyou will turn in to me:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol"><span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: "Times New Roman";"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol"><span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: "Times New Roman";"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol"><span style="font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; font-family: "Times New Roman";"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Courier