ter" style="text-align:center"></p><p class="MsoNormal">Watch these videos. Write a thoughtful paragraph about AI inbeef cattle. If you had cattle would you use AI? Explain why or why not.<o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><br></p>', '', 'other_cause', 'Work Conference', 'Claude Hebron', '2017-03-15', '', '0000-00-00', '', '0000-00-00'),
