(41, 'Vicky Williams', '2015-08-31', '2015-2016', 'dmatthews@sampsoncc.edu', '<p class="MsoNormal"><u>1. To design andbuild new courses that will help student be able to obtain certification  in Medical Billing & Coding. <o:p></o:p></u></p><u><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">2. To update Moodle to reflect new textbook forMedical Billing and Coding.        </span></u>', '<p class="MsoNormal"><u>1. To continue tosearch for resources that will allow student opportunities to experience actual billing process in Medical Billing and Coding. .  <o:p></o:p></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u>2. To designMoodle to incorporate new study resources and internet links that will help  students get a better understanding of newMedical Billing & Coding procedures.<o:p></o:p></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u>3. To obtaincertification in Medical Billing and Coding and help students learn how to  obtain certification in Medical Billing andCoding.       <o:p></o:p></u></p>', 'Vicky Williams', 'W. Darell Matthews'),
