2.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>I am very glad that we have a new instructor for the spring semester.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>The advising and registration of existing students was challenging but successful. Then new checklists for the students helped a lot and made registration and advising easier.</span></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u><span style="font-family:" times="" new="" roman",serif"="">3.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>I taught both NOS 130 and NOS 230 last semester and introduced Server 2012. Even though I will continue teaching Server 2008 this semester I plan on using a new book for Server 2012 in Fall2016 </span></u></p><p class="MsoNormal"><u><span style="font-family:" times="" new="" roman",serif"="">4.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>With making more of our classes Web Assisted and Hybrid, <span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span>Moodle has become more useful.Even though there were several changes in the platform, very little training was needed . </span></u></p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>', 'Al is always willing to step up and do more than what is required. &nbsp;His experience proves to be a valuable asset to our department and division on a regular basis. &nbsp;Students enjoy his courses and continue to rate his teaching very favorably.', '<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml> <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>  <o:TargetScreenSize>800x600</o:TargetScreenSize> </o:OfficeDocumentSettings></xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml> <w:WordDocument>  <w:View>Normal</w:View>  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>  <w:TrackMoves></w:TrackMoves>  <w:TrackFormatting></w:TrackFormatting>  <w:PunctuationKerning></w:PunctuationKerning>  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas></w:ValidateAgainstSchemas>  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>  <w:DoNotPromoteQF></w:DoNotPromoteQF>  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOthe